    "We begin by comparing the results of using AI agents to conduct the streetlight experiment with those obtained from human participants in online lab experiments.",
    "The results of this exercise are presented in Figure 3.",
    "The first primary outcome of interest is the group payoff (Panel A), which is the sum total of all individual payoffs in a group for a given round.",
    "We plot the mean group payoff across all rounds, as well as the 95% confidence intervals.",
    "The original results from the online lab experiment are presented in the upper left corner in plot i), which confirms the key prediction of the streetlight effect."
